OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAny mist or fog will quickly
OL,6,Fclear in the morning. Staying dry with
OL,7,Fsunny spells at first, but cloud
OL,8,Flikely increasing during the afternoon
OL,9,Fin the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FLargely cloudy during the start of the
OL,13,Fnew week with showers possible at
OL,14,Ftimes. Some brighter interlude are
OL,15,Falso possible, particularly in the
OL,16,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
